"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Excalibur_Mirage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/Excalibur\">Excalibur - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Excalibur\">Excalibur from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/mirage\">mirage - Wiktionary</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mirage\">Mirage from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mirage_(disambiguation)\">Mirage (disambiguation) from Wikipedia</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Excalibur_Mirage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Capture from the <a href=\"#Video\">Video</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=7591&amp;start=8\">Chess Products Ron Nelson designed/programmed</a> by <a href=\"/Ron_Nelson\" title=\"Ron Nelson\">ChessChallenger</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Hiarcs Forum</a>, January 11, 2016</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><